title: Text of rule for 7th-inning play in Rangers-Blue Jays
text: > Texas Text of rule for 7th-inning play in Rangers-Blue Jays Texas Rangers' Shin-Soo Choo, of South Korea, waits as the umpire crew discusses a play during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Toronto Blue Jays, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Toronto. The Blue Jays clinched their first trip to the American League Championship Series since 1993, overcoming one of the most bizarre plays in playoff history by taking advantage of three Rangers errors for a 6-3 victory. (Darren Calabrese/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
